_scope":"scope library 600-700 ex Daniel CEO directive verbatim 2026-05-13f \"faci handover dar vreau sa prinzi asta obligatoriu. E mandatory pre beta\"","revision_history":["rev1 2026-05-13e initial draft (Pillar 1 bodyweight lookup + Pillar 2 light variant 1:1 mapping + Pillar 3 pre-fatigue rules — flat fields schema too simple)","rev2 2026-05-13e cascade ordered list pattern locked Daniel principle \"Daca am tractiuni si nu pot -> helcometru. Daca nu am helcometru -> assisted pullup machine. Daca nu am -> variatie de exercitii fie 1 exercitiu sau 2, care sa acopere dezvoltarea musculara a grupei respective\" — Pillar 1+2 unified în fallback_cascade[] ordered list per exercise NU flat fields","locked-v2 2026-05-13f Co-CTO autonomous LANDED commit raw layer 03-decisions/ADR_SMART_ROUTING_EQUIPMENT_v2.md post chat ACASĂ Bundle 5 strategic complet — toate principles Daniel approved tacit (cascade ordered list per exercise + scope library 600-700 ex MANDATORY PRE-BETA + Andura primary gym-focused paradigm + light variant different-exercise-easier semantic + Co-CTO autonomy total trust delegation MAXIMUM). §2.2 mapping exemple representative illustrative — full ~600 ex library cascade populate Bundle 6.1 post Bundle 6.0.1-6.0.7 sub-batches library extension LANDED."]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[64,73],[170,200],[215,242]]},"smart_blocks:03-decisions/_FROZEN/ADR_SMART_ROUTING_EQUIPMENT_v2.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1ubxz2q","at":1778925830858},"key":"03-decisions/_FROZEN/ADR_SMART_ROUTING_EQUIPMENT_v2.md#---frontmatter---","lines":[1,15],"size":1820,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
